quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  11,24,"Fanano yezvikwata zviviri yakafanana neye bofu nematsi, neanoona neanonzwa. Vakaenzana here kana vakafananidzwa? Saka hamutori here chidzidzo"
  11,25,"Zvirokwazvo, takatumira Nowa kuvanhu vake (uye akati): “Ndauya kwamuri semuyambiri ari pachena.”"
  11,26,"“Kuti musanamate chimwe chinhu kunze kwaAllah; zvirokwazvo, ndokutyirai imi chirango chezuva remarwadzo.”"
  11,27,"Madzishe aisatenda pakati pevanhu vake akati: “Tinokuona asi semunhu akangofanana nesu, uye hationi vanokutevera vari kunze kweavo vasina maturo pakati pedu uye vasina kufunga. Uye hationi mauri muine chiremekedzo chinopfuura isu, asi pachokwadi tinokuona semunyepi.”"
  11,28,"Iye akati: “Imi vanhu vangu! Ndiudzei, ko kana ndine humboo huri pachena kubva kuna Tenzi vangu, uye vandipa tsitsi (chiporofita) kubva kwavari, asi (tsitsi) idzodzo dzakavanzwa mumaziso enyu. Tokumanikidzirai here kuchigamuchira (chitendero cheIslaam) imi muchichivenga?”"
  11,29,"“Uye imi vanhu vangu! Handina kukubvunzai hupfumi pamusoro pacho. Mubairo wangu hauna anawo kunze kwaAllah. Handisi kuzombofa ndakadzinga avo vanotenda. Zvirokwazvo, vachasangana naTenzi vavo, asi ndinokuonai muri vanhu vasina ruzivo.”"
  11,30,“Uye imi vanhu vangu! Ndiani achandibetsera kuna Allah kana ndikavadzinga? Hamurangarirewo here?”
  11,31,"“Uye handisi kuti kwamuri ndine hupfumi hwaAllah, kana kuti ndinoziva zvakavanzika, kana kuti ndiri kuti ini ndiri ngirozi, uye handisi kuti kune avo maziso enyu anovatarisira pasi kuti Allah havazovapi chakanaka. Allah vanoziva zviri mumoyo yavo. Zvirokwazvo, kana ndikadaro ndichave umwe wemaDhaalimoon (vatadzi).”"
  11,32,"Vakati: “Iwe Nowa! Wapikidzana nesu uye warebesa kupikidzana kwako nesu. Nokudaro tiunzire zvaunoti tyityidzira nazvo kana uri pachokwadi.”"
  11,33,"Iye akati: “Zvirokwazvo, Allah chete ndivo vachawaunza (marwadzo) kwamuri kana vachida, uye hamumbofi makapukunyuka.”"
  11,34,"“Uye yambiro yangu haikubetserei kunyange kana ndikashuvira kukupai zano rakanaka, kana kuda kwaAllah kuri kwekuti musave pagwara. Ndi Tenzi venyu uye kwavari muchadzokera.”"
  11,35,"Kana kuti avo (vasingatendi vemuMakkah) vanoti: “Uyu (Muhammad (SAW)) akarigadzira iri (Qur’aan).” Iti: “Kana ndakarigadzira, kwandiri ngakuve nemhosva yangu, asi handina mhosva pamhosva dzose dzamunoita.”"
  11,36,"Uye zvakazarurirwa Nowa: “Hapana pakati pevanhu vako vachatenda kunze kweavo vakatenda kare. Nokudaro usashungurudzike nezvavanoita.”"
  11,37,"“Uye vaka ngarava takakutarisa nemaziso edu uye nemashoko edu (nekuzarurirwa kwedu), uye usandidane uchimiririra avo vakaita zvakaipa; zvirokwazvo vachanyudzwa.”"
  11,38,"Uye paaivaka ngarava, pose-pose pavaimupfuura madzishe evanhu vake, vaimutsvinyira. Iye akati: “Kana mukatitsvinyira, saizvozvo tichakutsvinyiraiwo sematsvinyiro amuri kuita.”"
  11,39,"“Uye muchaziva kuti kuna ani kuchauya murango uyo uchamufukidza nenyadzi, uye kuna ani kuchawira murango usingaperi.”"
  11,40,"(Zvakava sokudaro) kusvika apo murairo wedu wakauya, uye hovhoni yakapfachuka (mvura ichibva pasi nesimba). Tikati: “Pinza mairi (ngarava) parudzi rwega rwega zviviri (hadzi nerume), uye nemhuri yako, kusara kweuyo shoko rakapfuura paari (kuti achaparadzwa), neavo vanotenda.” Uye hapana akatenda kwaari kunze kwevashoma"